  "body": "I think that in the Sol -> Yul translation, cleanup is not always done, at least not before equality comparison. Maybe we should do cleanup for every single type conversion?\r\n\r\nSpecifically, type conversion does not lead to cleanup when the types are the same. This could lead to problems with regards to inline assembly.",
